Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:06.21,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:11.39,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.....Rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:18.53,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今日が過去に変わる事で、明日が近づいて。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:25.78,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}そんな当たり前の事に　心は傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:29.86,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}あの日見た『世界』を　もう一度作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:35.35,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}叶う時が　いつか来るなら　もう何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:43.14,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}まるで可能性が無いと　誰に揶揄されても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:48.00,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}次の君に逢える日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:51.95,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繰り返し　巡る運命が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:55.31,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}たとえ　どんな道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.94,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}決して　決して　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:02.71,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}『あした、またね。』　その『未来』を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:06.50,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}いつまでも失くさないように
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:10.05,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}終わりのない始まり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:15.43,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今、君と夢見たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:20.18,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繋いだ手を　離さないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:23.36,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:27.03,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.24,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change.
